// Accents on mac ride bezelColor/contentTintColor (no NM_CUSTOMDRAW). The gallery's
// accent asserts are Win32-only in spirit; these keep the shared self-test compiling and
// return 0 (no stored COLORREF model on mac - the color lives on the NSButton).
